title: No Highway - Radio Drama
description:
2 X 60 mins

A two part dramatisation of the novel by the increasingly forgotten Nevil Shute.

Set in 1948, British designers have designed a revolutionary new passenger aircraft. However, the need to recoup development costs and the export drive mean that it may not have been tested sufficiently and may not be safe. This could almost have been a blue print for the "Comet" aircraft of the early fifties......
